{"tid":1365314,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［真心問] 元朗絲727去唔去","createTime":"2019-07-25T15:08:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T14:12:05.000Z","uid":282891,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"b2aa7f2ebe2c4a6ea386bbb8172748996de72894","tid":1365314,"uid":282891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:08:09.000Z","msg":"屋企人唔想我去 <br />\n但我覺得今日都唔敢出嚟<br />\n之後又點會贏<br />\n我唔想以後返屋企都要驚餐飽<br />\n我唔想以後朋友遲咗報平安到要徹夜難眠<br />\n我唔想元朗 甚至香港就咁冇咗<br />\n重要覺得背叛左山長水遠嚟守護我哋嘅一班義士<br />\n始終人多啲 每人相對都會安全啲<br />\n<br />\n理性話我知 我出嚟嘅風險較大<br />\n住元朗 重要係黑色地區<br />\n點相就gg 重會牽連埋我啲屋企人<br />\n啲黑社會真係冇人性架<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">理性感性不停掙扎 點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\nedit: 頭先typo柒咗所以repost"},{"pid":"707be0b8a92843cfabdaf0ea3b49bba2cc10ecb9","tid":1365314,"uid":50502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:09:50.000Z","msg":"留係和理非層撐人數"},{"pid":"fd357899c4276f2e2d752577c4d34e422ac9fe21","tid":1365314,"uid":256131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:10:35.000Z","msg":"做好保護措施就去 留喺中游位置"},{"pid":"09b222e5de20e2e4b006e89916a1bcee2830dd42","tid":1365314,"uid":91017,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:11:25.000Z","msg":"放心有pusst protector"},{"pid":"94c4310bd6359c248aad7c4637c07d0e62334717","tid":1365314,"uid":61396,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:12:32.000Z","msg":"大馬路 後排 <br />\n有事立即坐地鐵走人"},{"pid":"d02fb76b6896437195face6d45880eb8058e95a9","tid":1365314,"uid":11876,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:23:26.000Z","msg":"巴同你一樣住黑色地區，我諗住去<br />\n不過會做好d blackbloc, 帶黑cap, 頭巾，太陽眼鏡等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14dc4880405f08e6f73eef3efcb86901a56b152a","tid":1365314,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:31:00.000Z","msg":"唔洗驚 全民自衛